description: This skill chooses a fact at random from a list of cool facts, of varied genre, and tells it to you when asked to. The list of facts were chosen by the author from varied online resources and is limited to a small number.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask Cool Facts Now for a cool fact
Alexa, ask Cool Facts Now for a fact
name: myCoolFacts
shortDescription: A skill that tells cool facts
